IMAPAccount fastmail
Host imap.fastmail.com
Port 993
User julian@seemyvest.net
PassCmd "/home/julian/.local/bin/systemd-pass-fallback fastmail-app-password personal/fastmail/app-password"
TLSType IMAPS
TLSVersions +1.2

IMAPStore fastmail-remote
Account fastmail

MaildirStore fastmail-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/share/mail/fastmail/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/fastmail/Inbox

Channel fastmail
Far :fastmail-remote:
